VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (?i)^ENV\s+(?:PASSWORD|SECRET|API_KEY|APIKEY|TOKEN|ACCESS_KEY|PRIVATE_KEY|AUTH_TOKEN)\s*=?\s*\S
WHEN EXPR MISSING:placeholder|example|test|dummy|TODO && MISSING:ARG\s+\w+\s*$|--build-arg|SECRET_
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects secrets or credentials embedded as ENV instructions in Dockerfiles.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Secret Passed via ENV Instruction.
